1. *Biću* tu u pet. (I'll be here at five o'clock.)
2. *Bićemo* u stanu do pet. (We'll be at the apartment until five o'clock.)
3. *Bii* tamo pre nego što se vratimo. (Be there before we return.)
4. *Biću* spreman za pola sata. (I'll be ready in half an hour.)
5. *Biće* naše večere za pet minuta. (Our dinner will be ready in five minutes.)